### InventoryQuest — HTTP requests (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ .http)
@host = http://localhost:8080

### Actuator health
GET {{host}}/actuator/health

### Spawn a climber (302 → /game/{id}); copy the id from the Location header
POST {{host}}/spawn
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=Ada

### Set the player id you were redirected to
@player = PUT-THE-UUID-HERE

### The game screen (full page)
GET {{host}}/game/{{player}}

### Just this player's context panel (what the WebSocket nudge re-fetches)
GET {{host}}/game/{{player}}/panel

### Move around the ring
POST {{host}}/game/{{player}}/move
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

direction=RIGHT

### Dev: drop bots into the player's square so a vote can happen (dev profile only)
GET {{host}}/dev/bots?count=1&near={{player}}&vote=TRADE

### Cast a vote
POST {{host}}/game/{{player}}/vote
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

option=TRADE
